Requirements:

GNU Scientific Library: http://www.gnu.org/software/gsl/
FFTW: http://www.fftw.org/

Installation:

1. Check lib/Makefile and src/Makefile and modify PATHs accordingly.
2. cd lib; make clean; make
3. cd ../src ; make clean ; make
4. cd ../tools; make clean; make
4. Now copy tnl-dm3pes, tnl-lineshape, and tnl-dynamics in src/
   to a place that's accessible. For 2D job analysis, also copy
   tools/2dspec and tools/2danalysis.

Take a look at scripts/2d/README to see how to setup a 2D job.



